{"tid":2114384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"班仆街係我屋企開枝散葉","createTime":"2020-07-18T18:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T11:04:59.000Z","uid":303115,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"62d900c024e571be77e52b7b6b928498773e970c","tid":2114384,"uid":303115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T18:59:08.000Z","msg":"話說我屋企最近越來越多壁虎<br />\n有大條有細條<br />\n之前一開燈見到佢地真係嚇撚死<br />\n佢哋仲要同度門一樣色<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓豬我份人好細膽<br />\n最近入房都要望下啲牆先敢坐低<br />\n啱啱好開心睇完金秀賢套戲諗住去刷牙<br />\n一開門見到有啲嘢係我眼前幾cm跌落<br />\n望一望地下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母<br />\n係條壁虎bb<br />\n如果我企前少少佢就跌落去我塊面<br />\n或者我個波大少少佢就跣入我件衫入面<br />\n頂佢個肺<br />\n佢地越生越多<br />\n我住到好撚大壓力<br />\n點先可以趕走班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25bc1c50fe0ae863bfa57f8e075e2b2c09180f3","tid":2114384,"uid":304264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T19:01:21.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53174f754b533bfa4645e79827e13cca27b052df","tid":2114384,"uid":146574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T19:01:23.000Z","msg":"相呢？"},{"pid":"90db9efa66e25fa6f6b8114a4d48f323255c5eed","tid":2114384,"uid":232250,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T19:03:59.000Z","msg":"蛇仔明一走，下次就係大强同小强。"},{"pid":"15397fb67009ae76ff9c0a7c824e093acbc8f6e7","tid":2114384,"uid":249293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T19:04:05.000Z","msg":"你屋企多蚊 好食好住"},{"pid":"6386100b4e30ac147754dd8e0bed651f58981ff1","tid":2114384,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T19:04:30.000Z","msg":"叫左你過嚟同我住未無野囉"},{"pid":"b14b288b18c6d9fb90f23aaca9badcd1eaa0dd96","tid":2114384,"uid":90692,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T19:05:12.000Z","msg":"佢地好可愛，益蟲。"},{"pid":"60226